Privacy Policy:

At Resteez Rider, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. 
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose your data when you use our Resteez Rider application Resteez Rider available on the Google Play Store. 
By downloading and using the App, you agree to the terms and conditions outlined in this Privacy Policy.

Information Collection and Use:

1.1 Location: 
The App may request access to your device's location to provide location-based features.
We only collect your location data with your explicit permission, and we do not use or share this information for any other purposes without your consent.

1.2 Contact: 
The App may request access to your contacts to enable certain features like sharing content or inviting friends. 
We do not collect, store, or share your contact information without your explicit consent, and we only use this data within the App's functionalities.

1.3 Gallery: 
The App may request access to your device's gallery to allow you to upload or access images for specific features. 
We respect your privacy, and we do not access, collect, or share your gallery content without your explicit consent. 
Any images you upload or access within the App are solely used for the intended purposes.

1.4 Camera: 
The App may request access to your device's camera to enable features that require image or video capturing. 
We do not use your camera for any unauthorized purposes, and we do not collect or share any media captured by your device's camera without your explicit consent.

1.5 Location in the Background: 
The App may require access to your device's location even when it is running in the background to provide continuous location-based services.
We will obtain your explicit consent before collecting and using background location data, and we will only use this data to enhance your experience within the App.

Data Security:
We prioritize the security of your personal information and have implemented industry-standard measures to protect it from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Data Sharing:
We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your data with trusted third-party service providers that help us deliver and improve our services, subject to confidentiality obligations. 
We ensure that these service providers comply with appropriate data protection standards.

Children's Privacy:
The App is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. 
If you believe we have unintentionally collected information about a child, please contact us immediately, and we will promptly remove the data.

Changes to this Privacy Policy:
We reserve the right to modify or update this Privacy Policy from time to time. 
We will notify you of any changes by posting the revised version on the Google Play Store or within the App. 
Your continued use of the App after any modifications to this Privacy Policy will signify your acceptance of the changes.

Contact Us:
